            . I am shopman to Mr. Biddle, who lives in <placeName id="t18170416-29-crimeloc164">Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170416-29-crimeloc164" type="placeName" value="Bishopsgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18170416-29-crimeloc164" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-29-off162 t18170416-29-crimeloc164"></join>, opposite Mr. Stirtevant's. On the 28th of March, I saw the prisoner and another man lurking about his shop. The other man took the flannell from the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181704160014"></xptr>pile on the step of the shop. The prisoner took his apron, and folded it round the flannell, and walked off with it. I seized him, and took it from him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
